                  range, low noise, low consumption, high precision
                  and large number of read-out channels. This ASIC is
                  a very front-end read-out chip that integrates 36
                  self triggered channels with variable gain to
                  achieve charge and time measurements. The charge
                  measurement must be performed from 1 up to 2000
                  photo-electrons (p.e.) corresponding to 160 fC up to
                  320 pC for SiPM gain 10 6 . The time measurement is
                  performed with a coarse 12-bit counter related to
