                  (SPIROC2c) was submitted in February 2012 to improve
                  the noise performance and also to integrate a new
                  TDC (Time to Digital Converter) structure. This
                  paper describes SPIROC2 and SPIROC2c ASICs and
                  illustrates the main characteristics thank to a
